      <title>长江基建伦敦开盘后股价走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hong-kong-s-ck-infrastructure-sees-thin-trading-in-london-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长江基建集团有限公司 (CK Infrastructure Holdings Ltd.) 股价在伦敦首次亮相时上涨，但作为根据旨在吸引外国发行人前往英国首都的新规则实施的首次重大上市，交易相对清淡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hong-kong-s-ck-infrastructure-sees-thin-trading-in-london-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币下滑 难以利用全球风险偏好反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bitcoin-s-btc-august-drop-leaves-token-lagging-global-market-revival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管全球股市在摆脱对美国经济增长的担忧后回升至历史高位，但比特币和更广泛的加密货币市场本月迄今仍在大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bitcoin-s-btc-august-drop-leaves-token-lagging-global-market-revival</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 07:41:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
